  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wandshot is a 2D platformer where you have to make each shot count. With no jump button you have to rely on the kickback from your wand to traverse the various levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each world introduces new obstacles to master and ramps up the difficulty.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slightly less than 91 levels spanning 5 worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 200 crowns to collect</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At least 5 achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spikes...lots of Spikes</p></li></ul>",
